title: Ep229 Kink Crimes
description: Ep229 Kink Crimes is OUT NOW!!!  This week, the gals get frisky discussing the world of alternative sexual proclivities. Open a fresh bottle of Winc's Akoya Chardonnay, establish a safe word, and tune in for Kink Crimes. For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
